h","text":"百虑重忧，谓我何书，恸念来日，血泪交浴。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"43aee7c151"},{"id":"5d6bec2a65","type":"paragraph","text":"已歌燕市，无惭楚囚，子期不见，江波悠游！","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"43aee7c151"},{"id":"c7f92ffa24","type":"paragraph","text":"愁不能辍，愤不忍说，节不见改，志不可夺！","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"43aee7c151"},{"id":"16cc1731fd","type":"paragraph","text":"书愤沥血，明志绝泣，此身如絮，此心似铁！","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"43aee7c151"},{"id":"b127f3380f","type":"paragraph","text":"自由无价，年命有涯，宁为玉碎，以殉中华！","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"43aee7c151"},{"id":"0c2ebd33d5","type":"paragraph","text":"山川挝鼓，河岳鸣笳，魂化雷电，肠断桑麻！","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"43aee7c151"},{"id":"52ed18fa3b","type":"paragraph","text":"风雨长霄，平旦匪还，捐生取义，岂俟来朝！","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"43aee7c151"},{"id":"02b40c34f0","type":"paragraph","text":"志节皓皓，行状皎皎，正气凛冽，清名孔昭！","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"43aee7c151"},{"id":"37efd2bfca","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《林昭文抄》，甘粹先生2000年7月11日抄本。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"43aee7c151"}],"page":{"id":"0a38fe668f","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"43aee7c151","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}